<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Plataforma Suspendida</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .suspendida-card {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center min-vh-100">
    <div class="card shadow suspendida-card">
        <div class="card-body text-center">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle fa-3x text-warning mb-3"></i>
            <h1 class="card-title mb-3">Plataforma Suspendida</h1>
            <p class="card-text fs-5">La plataforma está suspendida por falta de pago.</p>
            <p class="card-text">Llevas <strong>2 días</strong> de retraso en tu pago.</p>
            <p class="card-text">Por favor, realiza el pago lo antes posible para reactivar el servicio.</p>
            <a href="/pago" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg mt-3">
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS Bundle -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
